      public static String createFile​(String name, String previousFileId, Path unencryptedFile, long fileSize, String language, String userId, String documentId) throws Exception
      Create a new file.
      Parameters:
      name - File name, can be null
      previousFileId - ID of the previous version of the file, if the new file is a new version
      unencryptedFile - Path to the unencrypted file
      fileSize - File size
      language - File language, can be null if associated to no document
      userId - User ID creating the file
      documentId - Associated document ID or null if no document
      Returns:
      File ID
      Throws:
